      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>TimeSkip is a Chrome and Edge browser extension that enables users to navigate through the posting history of X (Twitter) profiles by constructing date-filtered Advanced Search queries. The extension injects a widget onto X profile pages that allows users to select a time period and jump directly to posts from that date range. TimeSkip does not use the Twitter API or scrape any data — it leverages X's public Advanced Search feature.</p>

